name: Super Sky World 64
description:
Super Sky World 64 is a simple game about sailing and shooting.

Controls: 

Mouse: Aim, Shoot

A,D: Steer

If you are stuck on the normal boss, know that you can shoot the small cannons to temporarily disable them.

If you like the music, I uploaded it here:

https://soundcloud.com/muse-score/super-sky-world-64-theme
